    "Therefore, it is necessary to select and intensively investigate the most prominent features among numerous variables.",
    "MFCC is the result of imitating human audible frequency resolution by converting linear frequencies to logarithmic low frequencies, which can prevent training overfitting of deep learning networks and improve recognition accuracy by densely analyzing only key attributes of the eigengraph 59, 60.",
